able to that of hidden Markov models at a substantially\nlower computational cost.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Jun 2009 00:49:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Jul 2009 18:36:12 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 5 May 2010 22:57:42 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 7 May 2010 00:31:35 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 10 Jan 2011 07:41:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-01-11"}
