he \"Roper\" remains heavier than the odd-parity\n$[70,1^{-}]$-plet in all of our approximations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Jun 2009 13:51:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-08-13"}
